    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135090/extras/59b70b81a8b5224c9d64f91030c96b9b.avif?t=1725960495\" width=616 height=198 /></span><br><br>Your task is to control a drill that can dig down and collect resources. The deeper you drill, the more resources you can collect. But beware: there may be buried bombs on the way that can destroy your drill.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135090/extras/8d271d1bce3c5f0246202506062f4849.poster.avif?t=1725960495\" width=616 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135090/extras/8d271d1bce3c5f0246202506062f4849.webm?t=1725960495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135090/extras/8d271d1bce3c5f0246202506062f4849.mp4?t=1725960495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can upgrade your drill to dig deeper and collect more resources. To do this, you need to collect the resources you encounter on the way. You can also use the drill upgrade menu, which opens when you press Enter.<br><br>The controls are simple and intuitive: you can dig down with the S key or Space, and control the direction of the drill with the A and D keys.<br>The goal of the game is to set a record for drilling depth by avoiding bombs and collecting as many resources as possible.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135090/extras/5b3585c52d2f1f3945a1cf10ce194e28.poster.avif?t=1725960495\" width=616 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135090/extras/5b3585c52d2f1f3945a1cf10ce194e28.webm?t=1725960495\" type=